                        subMenuNode = "<div id='subMenu" + submenuID + "' class='column bgblue'><ul><li style='display: none'><span class='menuColSubHeading'></span></li></ul>";

                    else { subMenuNode = "<div id='subMenu" + submenuID + "' class='column'><ul><li style='display: none'><span class='menuColSubHeading'></span></li></ul>"; }
                }
                else {
                    if (DispColor == "1") {
                        subMenuNode = "<div id='subMenu" + submenuID + "' class='column bgblue'><ul><li><span class='menuColSubHeading'>" + subMenuItemHtml + "</span></li></ul>";
                    }
                    else { subMenuNode = "<div id='subMenu" + submenuID + "' class='column'><ul><li><span class='menuColSubHeading'>" + subMenuItemHtml + "</span></li></ul>"; }

                /*   if (menuIndex % 3 == 0) {

                submenuTbl += "";
                submenuTbl += subMenuNode;
                submenuTbl += GenerateMenuLink(submenuID);

                submenuTbl += "";
                count++; menuIndex++;
                if (menuIndex % 3 == 0) {
                    submenuTbl += "<br style='clear: left' />";
                }
            }
        });

        return submenuTbl;

    }

<link href="/Style%20Library/en-us/Core%20Styles/NPCorporate/jquery.bxslider.css" rel="stylesheet" />

<!--<script type='text/javascript' src='../SiteAssets/infinite-rotator.js'></script>-->
<script type="text/javascript">
    var imgs = [];
    var imgHrefs = [];
    var cnt = 0;
    var intervals = 10; //default 5 sec(s)
    var currentItem = 0;
    var imgTitles = [];
    var bx = jQuery.noConflict();
    $(document).ready(function () {
        var rotationSpeed = document.getElementById('ctl00_SPWebPartManager1_g_11731dfd_fe89_48a7_b4a8_8d8d13bd5984_hdnRotationSpeed').value;
        FillSliderImgs(rotationSpeed);
    });
    function FillSliderImgs(rotationSpeed) {

        var picture = '';
        var imgsrc = '';
        var picHyperlink = '#';
        var imgTitle = '';
        var imgID = '';
        var sImgBind = '';
        var sClickableImgURL = '';
        var rootSiteURL = window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.host + "/";
        var sul = "<ul class='bxslider'>";

        //$(xData.responseXML).SPFilterNode("z:row").each(function () {
        $(".imgSliderClass1").each(function () {
            picture = $(this).attr("ows_RequiredField");
            imgsrc = rootSiteURL + picture;
            imgTitle = $(this).attr("ows_Description");
            sClickableImgURL = $(this).attr("ows_URL");
            imgID = $(this).attr("ows_ID");
            imgs.push(imgsrc);

            picHyperlink = $(this).attr("ows_URL");

            if (picHyperlink != undefined && picHyperlink != "") {
                picHyperlink = picHyperlink.split(",")[0];
            }
            imgHrefs.push();
            if (imgTitle != undefined && imgTitle != "") {
                imgTitle = imgTitle;
            }
            else {
                imgTitle = "";
            }
            imgTitles.push(imgTitle);

            if (typeof (picHyperlink) != "undefined" && picHyperlink != undefined && picHyperlink != "") {
                sImgBind += "<li id='firimg" + imgID + "'><a href='" + picHyperlink + "' id='imgLink'  style='display:block;' alt='' title='" + imgTitle + "'><img id='imageSlide' alt=''  src='" + imgsrc + "' /></a></li>"
            }
            else {
                sImgBind += "<li id='firimg" + imgID + "'><img id='imageSlide' alt='' title='' src='" + imgsrc + "' /></li>"
            }

        }); // end completefunc
        cnt = imgs.length;
        // var sImgBind1 = "<li><a href='#' id='imgLink'  style='display:block;' title=''><img id='imageSlide' alt=''  src='../../SiteCollectionImages/3.png' /></a></li><li><a href='#' id='A1'  style='display:block;' title=''><img id='Img1' alt=''  src='../../SiteCollectionImages/2.png' /></a></li>";
        sul += sImgBind + "</ul>";
        //document.getElementById("imgDiv").innerHTML = sImgBind1;
        $("#imgDiv").append(sImgBind);

        var slider = bx('#imgDiv.bxslider').bxSlider({
            auto: true,
            autoStart: true,
            randomStart: false,
            pause: rotationSpeed * 1000
        });
        var wait = rotationSpeed * 1000;
        //setTimeout(function () { slider.startAuto(); }, wait);
        setTimeout(function () { slider.startAuto(); }, wait);
        //if (rotationSpeed > 0) {
        //     slider.speeed = rotationSpeed * 1000;
        // }
        $('#pronext').click(function () {
            slider.goToNextSlide();
            // slider.stopAuto();
            setTimeout(function () { slider.startAuto(); }, wait);
            return false;
        });


        $('#proprev').click(function () {

            slider.goToPrevSlide();
            //slider.stopAuto();
            setTimeout(function () { slider.startAuto(); }, wait);
            return false;
        });
    }



    function Slider() {
        $('#imageSlide').fadeOut("slow", function () {
            if (cnt > 0) {
                //$(this).attr('src', imgs[currentItem]);
                $(this).attr('src', imgs[currentItem]).fadeIn("slow");
                $('#imgLink').attr('href', imgHrefs[currentItem]);
                $('#imgLink').attr('title', imgTitles[currentItem]);
                if (currentItem == cnt - 1) {
                    currentItem = 0;
                } else {
                    currentItem++;
                }
            }
        });

    }

</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    var imgs1 = [];
    var imgHrefs1 = [];
    var cnt1 = 0;
    var intervals1 = 10; //default 5 sec(s)
    var currentItem1 = 0;
    var imgTitles1 = [];
    var bx1 = jQuery.noConflict();
    var currentSite1 = '';
    $(document).ready(function () {
        var rotationSpeed2 = document.getElementById('ctl00_SPWebPartManager1_g_ca4400d5_e539_4d07_b97f_609215cb3a94_hdnRotationSpeed2').value;
        FillSliderImgs2(rotationSpeed2);

    });
    function FillSliderImgs2(rotationSpeed2) {

        var rootSiteURL2 = window.location.protocol + "//" + window.location.host + "/";
        var picture1 = '';
        var imgsrc1 = '';
        var picHyperlink1 = '#';
        var imgTitle1 = '';
        var imgID = '';
        var sImgBind1 = '';
        var sClickableImgURL1 = '';
        var sul1 = "<ul class='bxslider'>";
       

        $(".imgSliderClass2").each(function () {
            picture1 = $(this).attr("ows_RequiredField");
            imgsrc1 = rootSiteURL2 + picture1;
            imgTitle1 = $(this).attr("ows_Description");
            imgID = $(this).attr("ows_ID");
            sClickableImgURL1 = $(this).attr("ows_URL");
            imgs1.push(imgsrc1);

            picHyperlink1 = $(this).attr("ows_URL");

            if (picHyperlink1 != undefined && picHyperlink1 != "") {
                picHyperlink1 = picHyperlink1.split(",")[0];
            }
            imgHrefs1.push();
            if (imgTitle1 != undefined && imgTitle1 != "") {
                imgTitle1 = imgTitle1;
            }
            imgTitles1.push(imgTitle1);
            if (typeof (picHyperlink1) != "undefined" && picHyperlink1 != undefined && picHyperlink1 != "") {
                sImgBind1 += "<li id='secimg" + imgID + "'><a href='" + picHyperlink1 + "' id='imgLink1'  style='display:block;' alt='' title='" + imgTitle1 + "'><img id='imageSlide1' usemap='#maptest1' alt=''  src='" + imgsrc1 + "' /></a></li>"
            }
            else {
                sImgBind1 += "<li id='secimg" + imgID + "'><img id='imageSlide1' usemap='#maptest1' alt=''  src='" + imgsrc1 + "' /></li>"
            }

            //alert(sImgBind1);

        });  
        cnt1 = imgs1.length;
        // var sImgBind1 = "<li><a href='#' id='imgLink'  style='display:block;' title=''><img id='imageSlide' alt=''  src='../../SiteCollectionImages/3.png' /></a></li><li><a href='#' id='A1'  style='display:block;' title=''><img id='Img1' alt=''  src='../../SiteCollectionImages/2.png' /></a></li>";
        sul1 += sImgBind1 + "</ul>";
        //document.getElementById("imgDiv").innerHTML = sImgBind1;
        $("#imgDiv1").append(sImgBind1);

        var slider1 = bx1('#imgDiv1.bxslider').bxSlider({
            auto: true,
            autoStart: true,
            randomStart: false,
            pause: rotationSpeed2 * 1000
        });
        var wait1 = rotationSpeed2 * 1000;

        setTimeout(function () { slider1.startAuto(); }, wait1);
        $('#pronext1').click(function () {

            slider1.goToNextSlide();
            setTimeout(function () { slider1.startAuto(); }, wait1);
            return false;
        });

        $('#proprev1').click(function () {

            slider1.goToPrevSlide();
            setTimeout(function () { slider1.startAuto(); }, wait1);
            return false;
        });
    }
 

    //    function Slider() {
    //        $('#imageSlide').fadeOut("slow", function () {
    //            if (cnt > 0) {
    //                $(this).attr('src', imgs[(imgs.length++) % cnt]).fadeIn("slow");
    //            }
    //        });
    //    }

    function Slider1() {
        $('#imageSlide1').fadeOut("slow", function () {
            if (cnt > 0) {
                //$(this).attr('src', imgs[currentItem]);
                $(this).attr('src', imgs[currentItem1]).fadeIn("slow");
                $('#imgLink1').attr('href', imgHrefs[currentItem1]);
                $('#imgLink1').attr('title', imgTitles[currentItem1]);
                if (currentItem1 == cnt1 - 1) {
                    currentItem1 = 0;
                } else {
                    currentItem1++;
                }
            }
        });

    }

</script>
